    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Thanks. It sounds like you're saying the risk is pretty much a given. What about the people who say focusing on \"existential risk\" is just a distraction from more immediate issues or that it's mostly speculative? Is there any substance to their side, or is that just avoiding the real dangers?",
